  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2637990/extras/7c0bfdad496ad0c40becbfd0dfb7fdad.poster.avif?t=1765295539\" width=600 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2637990/extras/7c0bfdad496ad0c40becbfd0dfb7fdad.webm?t=1765295539\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2637990/extras/7c0bfdad496ad0c40becbfd0dfb7fdad.mp4?t=1765295539\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2637990/extras/af3a6de7323b3c9b577384a32024cc79.webp?t=1765295539\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2637990/extras_big/af3a6de7323b3c9b577384a32024cc79.webp?t=1765295539 width=800 height=41 /></span><i> </i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2637990/extras/f98c95ca202dfd26504851c355883aa4.webp?t=1765295539\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2637990/extras_big/f98c95ca202dfd26504851c355883aa4.webp?t=1765295539 width=800 height=41 /></span><i> <br>Aggretsuko meets Return of the Obra Dinn in Duck Detective, a cozy mystery game about a down-on-his-luck duck searching for answers in a sinister sausage-based conspiracy.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2637990/extras/98f93ea51bf648232eef3be10121236b.poster.avif?t=1765295539\" width=600 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2637990/extras/98f93ea51bf648232eef3be10121236b.webm?t=1765295539\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2637990/extras/98f93ea51bf648232eef3be10121236b.mp4?t=1765295539\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2637990/extras/38c6d8df9c60f8556e1a65fe2e63c58a.webp?t=1765295539\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2637990/extras_big/38c6d8df9c60f8556e1a65fe2e63c58a.webp?t=1765295539 width=800 height=41 /></span><i> <br>Join the Duck Detective on his latest, greatest case:</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i> </i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Inspect and interview suspects to learn their hidden secrets, then use the information you’ve gathered (plus your own de-duck-tive reasoning) to locate the suspect and bust the case wide open!</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2637990/extras/3b8c8ce88eba9f737ac35754d4f9a855.poster.avif?t=1765295539\" width=600 height=198 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2637990/extras/3b8c8ce88eba9f737ac35754d4f9a855.webm?t=1765295539\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2637990/extras/3b8c8ce88eba9f737ac35754d4f9a855.mp4?t=1765295539\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2637990/extras/6a944fdb9b1a77cf1f5cbfcdbd6fbdae.webp?t=1765295539\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2637990/extras_big/6a944fdb9b1a77cf1f5cbfcdbd6fbdae.webp?t=1765295539 width=800 height=41 /></span><i></i></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A 2-3 hour long mystery game!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Interview suspects, fill in the blanks and crack the case!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fully voice-acted! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Throw bread to the fine beak of lady justice!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Judge everyone on first impressions, just by looking at them really, really hard! Get them to admit things by staring! Do ducks blink? You don’t.<i></i></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2637990/extras/71e6dc3273f25f54c4c41be1a97249a0.poster.avif?t=1765295539\" width=600 height=188 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2637990/extras/71e6dc3273f25f54c4c41be1a97249a0.webm?t=1765295539\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2637990/extras/71e6dc3273f25f54c4c41be1a97249a0.mp4?t=1765295539\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></i></p>",
